profile: Hello, my name is Rick Unrau, owner/operator of Rick's Pest Control. I started this buisness because as a young boy I saw first hand the damage generated by pests such as gophers, moles, pigeons and coyotes done to farm land/barnyards. I had a dream to start up a pest control service that helps farmers, buisness and rural areas. I've always liked to hunt and fish which lead me to putting this company together. I have been in operation for 7.5yrs and am fully certified and licensed to exterminate and capture pest and remove them from premises.
